{
  "id": "adv_group_tri_03_05",
  "title": "TRINITYAiLE 03 05",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_05-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "このパフォーマンス勝負、勝ったのは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The winner of this performance battle is…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_05-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "優ちゃんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yu-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.96000008583069,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 3.9600000858306936
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 5.326666752497353
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_05-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "え……？　ほんまに？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh…? Really?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.326666752497356,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 8.493333419164024
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_05-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "うん。採点はすごく僅差だったけど……\n優ちゃんの合計点が上だった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. It was really close…\nBut Yu-chan’s total score was higher.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.793333419164023,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 14.123871992404263
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_05-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルを存続させたいから、とかは抜きに\n純粋なパフォーマンス勝負で、優ちゃんの勝ちだったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Setting aside the fact that I wanted TRINITYAiLE to continue‚\nYu-chan won the pure performance battle.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.92387199240427,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 20.940924356753634
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 24.90469402397673
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_05-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "そっか……良かった……\n聞いてた、瑠依ちゃん？　これで文句ないやろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… That’s good…\nDid ya hear that‚ Rui-chan? No complaints now‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.907591023420306,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 29.96291391601166
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_05-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "うん……さすがだったわ\n思っていた通り……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes… You were amazing.\nJust as I expected…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.462913916011665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 34.32628626289468
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_05-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "……え？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.32628626289468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 35.38628626527887
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_05-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "それが優の、本気だったんだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That was your true potential‚ Yu.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.38628626527887,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 38.69567394914728
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_05-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "な……なんでそんな、笑ってんの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-Why… Why are you smiling like that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.69567394914728,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 41.97254467668634
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_05-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "当たり前じゃない\n優がやっと、私に対して本気を出してくれた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Isn’t it obvious?\nYou finally showed me your true self‚ Yu.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.63921134335303,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 47.239211341614556
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_05-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "私達のために、全力になってくれた\nそれが嬉しいからよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You gave it your all for us.\nI’m happy about that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.60587800828123,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 52.73881257859373
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_05-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.73881257859373,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 54.21881259766722
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_05-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "優が優なりに\nトリエルのことを考えてくれていたのは伝わった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can tell that you were thinking of TRINITYAiLE\nin your own way‚ Yu.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.75214593100055,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_05-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "それには感謝もしているし……\n本気にさせようとしてヒドいことを言ったのは、謝るわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m grateful for that…\nAnd I apologize for saying those horrible things to try and get you to be serious.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.12613687999552,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 65.12613690444871
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_05-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "でも、トリエルのためとか私のためとか\nそんな寂しい答え、本当は聞きたくなかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I didn’t really want to hear that kind of lonely answer‚\nabout doing it for TRINITYAiLE or for me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.09280357111535,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 73.30182850906296
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_05-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "三人が揃って、全力を出さないとたどり着けない場所\nそれが、私達の目指しているトップアイドルでしょう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The place we’re aiming for‚ the place we can only reach if all three of us give it our all‚\nthat’s what it means to be top idols‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.93516184239628,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 81.90182889053267
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_05-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "そう……やな\n全部、瑠依ちゃんの言う通りやったかもしれんわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s… right.\nYou might be right about everything‚ Rui-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.50182889053266,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 89.44690878290972
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_05-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "でも、仕方ないねん。周りの顔色うかがって\n誰かのために自分をセーブする",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it can’t be helped. I’ve always been reading people’s expressions‚\nand holding myself back for the sake of others.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.48024211624308,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 99.96898041031302
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_05-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "うちは、そうすることしか出来んかったから……\nこの生き方は……呪いなんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because that’s all I’ve ever been able to do…\nThis way of life… is a curse.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.96898041031302,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 103.08953598575336
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_05-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "呪い……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A curse…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.08953598575336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 104.42286931908671
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_05-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "簡単な話です……うちの母は誰もが知ってる女優で\n昔からいろんな目で見られてきて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s a simple story… My mom is an actress that everyone knows‚\nand I’ve been seen in all sorts of ways since I was little…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.8134177779063,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 112.6989875269338
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_05-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "何かをして目立てば、出る杭打たれた\nそんな環境で生きてきたら、こうもなりますわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I did something that made me stand out‚ I was hammered down.\nIf you live in that kind of environment‚ this is what you become.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.46565419360051,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 120.75803244560012
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
